title: Want to learn Mid/Jungle from a Challenger? Here's your chance.
body:
Hey everyone, Zazuu here. A Challenger R5's/Master Tier SOloq Player from Season 4.
The following link has questions that will help me decide if I should start making tutorial videos for YOU.

https://www.surveymonkey.com/s/WNPCLW6

Answering the questions will give YOU the opportunity to have the knowledge of a Challenger Player, helping you climb the Solo q ladder and show off that Shiny Diamond boarder to your friends.


For any other questions just ask me here and I'll do my best to respond to them.

Thanks,
Zazuu.
